{"tid":1957763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海外返港年輕女子居家隔離曾發燒今早呼吸困難送院時不治","createTime":"2020-04-04T06:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T06:50:32.000Z","uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae458d86681b7c0e9f2dcf8b9b7637006b61698","tid":1957763,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:50:12.000Z","msg":"有公立醫院醫護人員向《立場》透露，一名20多歲女子，3月中從海外返港，4月初完成十四日居家檢疫，期間曾發燒但無通知衛生署，今早呼吸困難送院，送到大埔那素醫院前死亡，已抽取樣本檢驗死者是否染武漢肺炎。消息指死者3月中返港，4月2日完成居家檢疫，期間曾發燒數日，無通知衛生署，但曾到中醫求診，目前正檢測是否感染武漢肺炎，預計今晚有結果。"},{"pid":"d851f11fc5379cf497f55215416fec9c3c30e094","tid":1957763,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:50:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E8%BF%94%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90-%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%B6%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E6%9B%BE%E7%99%BC%E7%87%92-%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A9%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E5%9B%B0%E9%9B%A3%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB-%E6%AD%A3%E6%AA%A2%E9%A9%97%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25BF%2594%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590-%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2587%2592-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%2591%25BC%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%259B%25B0%25E9%259B%25A3%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2596%2593%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E9%25A9%2597%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%2F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=7d20a0b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B6